therapeutic tool.

00:06:52.630 --> 00:06:55.070 align:middle line:90%
It is a powerful tool.

00:06:55.070 --> 00:06:56.540 align:middle line:90%
It's very sacred.

00:06:56.540 --> 00:07:00.910 align:middle line:84%
It requires huge trust, and
it is a massive responsibility

00:07:00.910 --> 00:07:04.730 align:middle line:84%
